HEADWORD: Tour
<hw>Tour</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>tour</ets>. See
<er>Tower</er>.]</ety> <def>A tower.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
